    "In spite of this, it is important to recognize that ChatGPT has a number of limitations such as the potential provision of false and inaccurate answers to questions in specific VR categories, especially in clinical reasoning questions.",
    "The model is trained on an updated version of ChatGPT from 2021 and is influenced by the abundance of information available online rather than by recent and reliable sources.",
    "Medical professionals should therefore use this tool carefully and be aware of its limitations."
